{
  "stem": "1216.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Those 300 people in one room came from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It went all the way from what used to be called lower, lower class to really high up higher class kind of people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I hate to use those terms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But at that time they made sense.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not everybody had the same hygiene upbringing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some people washed every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some people washed once a month.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, these things happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So fleas had a good time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We did not, but they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One of the things we all had to learn was catch and kill, naturally.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then they got entangled in the blankets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We did not have sheets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had the-- the straw mattress, a straw pillow, no sheets, and the blankets which we'd brought from home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the fleas get entangled in those European wool blankets, and they're almost impossible to get out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So that was one of the relatively minor problems.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "At the end of each barracks, on the short end, was a washroom, one for the men, one for the women, with, running down the middle, a metal long sink, all over the whole length of the washroom, with faucets about, oh, I guess every three feet.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Yeah, about a meter between them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Cold water only.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were supposed to use that for washing ourselves, for washing our clothes, for washing anything and everything that needed washing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And somewhere in a corner was a toilet, either a flush toilet, which mostly didn't work, or what we would now call a chemical toilet-- I don't know what they were called then -- for the 300 people.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And again, as I said earlier, standing in line was normal for that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They also had outhouses, again, with standing in line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Equally, if not more disagreeable.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
